reviewText: good condition. good movies to expand the halo universe

I am not sure exactly how to review this product.  If I was review it by the movies I would give this deal 3 start because FUD was pretty good and Nightfall was not great.  However, paying $10 is a good deal considering FUD cost $8.99 itself on Amazon at the moment.  (Nightfall current costs $14.39).  So the deal overall with the movies included I believes deserves 4 stars.
